              "title": "Teams",
              "value": "\"Summarize this chat: decisions, risks, and next steps.\""
            },
            {
              "title": "Word",
              "value": "\"Turn these notes into a 1-page brief with headings and bullets.\""
            },
            {
              "title": "PowerPoint",
